tiers.ability_description: Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn, for each enemy with fewer than 4 debuffs, that ally gains 30% Potency until the end of the turn.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.

The first time each Hutt Cartel ally falls below 50% Health, they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn, which can't be copied, dispelled, or prevented.\n\nWhenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, Hutt Cartel allies recover 5% Health and Protection, gain 5% Turn Meter, and there is a 50% chance that enemy is inflicted with a Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, prevented, or resisted.

The max cooldown of Inventive is reduced by 1. Whenever Boushh inflicts Thermal Detonators on an enemy, inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns and Hutt Cartel allies gain 10% Armor Penetration (max 70%) and 10% Turn Meter (once per turn).
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn, for each enemy with fewer than 4 debuffs, that ally gains 30% Potency until the end of the turn.
The first time each Scoundrel ally uses a Basic ability on their turn, reset their cooldowns and gain 100% Turn Meter. Limit once per character per battle.

Whenever a Tusken ally critically hits an enemy, the enemy gains 1% Turn Meter. Whenever an enemy takes damage from a Damage Over Time effect, Tusken allies recover 10% Protection and gain 5% counter chance (stacking, max 100%). If a Tusken ally is active in the Leader slot, at the start of each turn, all enemies inflicted with a Damage Over Time effect can't recover Health.
Light Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever a debuff on an enemy expires, Jawa allies gain 2% Potency and Tenacity (stacking) until the end of battle.
The first time each Dark Side ally reaches 90%, 70%, and 50% Health inflict Doubt on a random enemy that doesn't have it for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled or prevented.
Whenever Light Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Whenever Rebel Fighter allies grant a buff to another ally, that ally gains 10% Turn Meter (limit once per turn per ally).
Whenever Light Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain a buff, they recover 2% Health and Protection.
At the start of their first turn, Empire allies gain Offense equal to 400% of their current Defense. Then they lose 50% Defense.
